WPiPAD 1.0

installation instructions:
1. put wpipad.php in wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. put 'slable' folder in wp-content/themes directory
3. activate the plugin

if you want to use your own iPad-friendly theme, simply edit wpipad.php on this line:

define("WPIPAD_THEME","slablet");

and change the word "slablet" to your favorite theme's folder name. Do not remove the quotation marks.

Guide on creating theme:
-if you want to make "view full site" link, simply link it to [your web url]/wpipadoff
-to view "view iPad site", simply link to [your web url]/wpipadon

however, the default view on iPad is iPad view.